	RELEASED: bedrock 2.0.2

	* configure.ac (AC_INIT): set version to 2.0.2 for release
	* NEWS: set release date on 2.0.2 news blurb

	* src/main/perl/lib/Bedrock/PDF/Maker.pm ($VERSION): Use
	  hard-coded value rather than a munging of the expansion of the
	  CVS 'Revision' keyword.
	* src/main/perl/lib/Bedrock/PDF/Handle.pm ($VERSION): likewise
	* src/main/perl/lib/Bedrock/Context/Shell.pm ($VERSION): likewise
	* src/main/perl/lib/Bedrock/SIS/Log.pm ($VERSION): likewise
	* src/main/perl/lib/Bedrock/SIS/Array.pm ($VERSION): likewise
	* src/main/perl/lib/Bedrock/SIS/Config.pm ($VERSION): likewise
	* src/main/perl/lib/Bedrock/SIS/InputSource/Term.pm ($VERSION): likewise
