	* src/main/bedrock/pebbles/simplemenu.peb
	* src/main/bedrock/pebbles/rbox.peb
	* src/main/bedrock/pebbles/linkbox.peb
	* src/main/bedrock/pebbles/selbox.peb


	CVS transplanted following files from tree rooted at
	Perl/Bedrock. Note that the subtree formerly at:
	    Perl/Bedrock/BLM
	has been migrated to:
	    src/main/perl/lib/BLM
	and /not/:
	    src/main/perl/lib/Bedrock/BLM
	This is to reflect the package names of the BLM modules, which are
	    BLM::Foo
	not
	    Bedrock::BLM::Foo
	* src/main/perl/lib/Bedrock/Text/TagX/Term.pm
	* src/main/perl/lib/Bedrock/Text/TagX/Error.pm
